I"Æ<p>The <code>websocket_api</code> sensor platform shows how many clients are connected to the stream API.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To add the connected clients to your installation, add the following to your <code>configuration.yaml</code> file:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
sensor:
  - platform: websocket_api
</code></pre>
<h3>Note</h3>
<p>This replaces the previous <code>api_streams</code> sensor.</p>
